  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the lentils and soak them in water for 30 minutes.",
    "Drain the lentils and cook them in a pot of boiling water until they are tender.",
    "Heat oil in a pan and saute the onion, ginger, and garlic until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the cumin seeds, coriander powder, and turmeric powder to the pan and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cooked lentils, white wine vinegar, and salt to the pan and stir well.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer the mixture for 10 minutes.",
    "Prepare the lotus leaves by washing and drying them.",
    "Spoon the lentil mixture onto the center of a lotus leaf and fold the leaf to form a parcel.",
    "Serve the pungent pickled Indian lentils Biryani hot, wrapped in the lotus leaf."
